      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide is for educational purposes only and does not constitute formal tax or legal advice. 280E is a complex federal law with significant penalties for non-compliance. Always work with a qualified Maine cannabis CPA or tax attorney.</em></p>
    </section>
